
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Donations";
}

<head>
    <link href="@Url.Content("~/Content/donations-css.css")" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="@Url.Content("~/Scripts/donations.js")" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <br />
    <br />
    <div class="image">
        <h1>D&nbsp;o&nbsp;n&nbsp;a&nbsp;t&nbsp;e</h1>
        <br />
        <br />
        <p><i>"The Earth is what we all have in common" - Wendell Berry</i></p>
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3" id="first-icon">
            <img src="~/Images/Donations-page/paypal.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3" id="second-icon">
            <img src="~/Images/Donations-page/divide.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3" id="third-icon">
            <img src="~/Images/Donations-page/coin.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3" id="fourth-icon">
            <img src="~/Images/Donations-page/gift.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3" id="fifth-icon">
            <img src="~/Images/Donations-page/divide.png" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-container">
        <div class="first">
            <div class="method-1"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/paypal.png"/></div>
            <div class="desc1">
                <h3>PAYPAL AND CREDIT CARD - DONATE IN ONE CLICK</h3>
                <p>Due to Paypal commission the minimum amount is 5€, and we would kindly ask you to give one amount once as opposed to several small amounts.</p>
                <br />
                <br />
                <button class="button" onclick="firstFunc()">Donate</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="second">
            <div class="desc2">
                <h3>DONATE WITH CRYPTO</h3>
                <p>Donating cryptocurrency is a non-taxable event, meaning you do not owe capital gains tax on the appreciated amount and can deduct it on your taxes. This makes Bitcoin and other cryptocurrency donations one of the most tax-efficient <br /> ways to support your favorite cause. If you have any question, please <a href="mailto:contact@weforest.org"></a>contact us.</p>
                <br />
                <br />
                <button class="button" onclick="secondFunc()">Donate</button>
            </div>
            <div class="method-2"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/divide.png" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="third">
            <div class="method-3"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/coin.png" /></div>
            <div class="desc3">
                <h3>MAKE A BANK TRANSFER</h3>
                <p>Please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@weforest.org">contact@weforest.org</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fourth">
            <div class="desc4">
                <h3>CHOOSE YOUR PROJECT ON GLOBAL GIVING</h3>
                <p>Grow trees in your chosen project by selecting from the options below.</p>
                <p>Global Giving is tax-efficient only for US residents. If you are a Europe resident and want to make a tax-efficient donation. please click here.</p>
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-items">
                        <div class="col">
                            <a href="https://www.weforest.org/project/brazil-wildlife-corridors"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/brazil.jpg" alt="brazil-landscape" /></a>
                            <div class="col-in">
                                <h1>Brazil, Wildlife Corridors</h1>
                                <p>Restoring the Antlantic Forest to bring back wildlife</p>
                                <button class="button" onclick="funcBrazilDonate()">Donate(USD)</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col">
                            <a href="https://www.weforest.org/project/ethiopia-desaa"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/ethiopia.jpg" alt="ethiopia-landscape" /></a>
                            <div class="col-in">
                                <h1>Ethipoia Desa'a</h1>
                                <p>Reversing land degradation and poverty through forest landscape restoration</p>
                                <button class="button" onclick="funcEthiopiaDonate()">Donate(USD)</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-out">
                        <a href="https://www.weforest.org/project/ethiopia-amhara"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/amhara.jpg" alt="amhara-ethiopia-landscape"/></a>
                        <div class="col-in">
                            <h1>Ethiopia Amhara</h1>
                            <p>A community-based approach to restore degraded lands</p>
                            <button class="button" onclick="funcAmharaDonate()">Donate(USD)</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="method-4"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/gift.png" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fifth">
            <div class="method-5"><img src="~/Images/Donations-page/divide.png" /></div>
            <div class="desc5">
                <h3>DONATE VIA TGE - FOR TAX EFFICIENT DONATIONS</h3>
                <p>
                    If you are a resident in any of the countries shown below, you may be able to maximise your gift through <br />Transnational Giving Europe (TGE). Just select the relevant tab below and follow the instructions.
                </p>
                <p>

                    TGE is a collaborative giving scheme offered by a partnership of European foundations. <br />It enables donors (both corporations and individuals) resident in one of the participating countries to offer financial support to non-profit organisations in other member countries. <br />Beneficiaries benefit directly from the tax advantages provided for in the legislation of their country of residence.
                </p>
                <p>

                    If you are resident in another European country and would like to donate a considerable amount <br />and benefit from tax deductibility, please <a href="mailto:contact@weforest.org">contact us</a>.
                </p>
                <div class="col-in">
                    <p><a onclick="funcBel()">Belgium, the Netherlands, Luxembourg or Denmark</a> | <a onclick="funcAus()">Australia and Hong Kong</a> | <a onclick="funcFra()">France</a> | <a onclick="funcGer()">Germany</a> | <a onclick="funcIta()">Italy</a> | <a onclick="funcSpa()">Spain</a> | <a onclick="funcSwi()">Switzerland</a> | <a onclick="funcUni()">United Kingdom</a> | <a onclick="funcUnis()">United States</a> | <a onclick="funcWF()">WF tax deductibility in other countries</a></p>
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    
                    <p id="demo"></p>
                    <p id="demo1"></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


</body>
